*The cellar below [[Varrock#Banks|Varrock West]] [[Bank]] - {{Map|name=Coins|mapID=12|3188,9820,qty:42|3188,9819,qty:26|3189,9819,qty:35|3190,9819,qty:56|3191,9821,qty:66|3195,9820,qty:4|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*[[Wine of zamorak]] in the [[Chaos Temple (Asgarnia)|Asgarnian Chaos Temple]] west of the [[Goblin Village]] - {{Map|name=Wine of zamorak|2930,3515|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*Wine of zamorak in the [[Chaos Temple (hut)|Wilderness Chaos Temple]] - {{Map|name=Wine of zamorak|2950,3824|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*Wine of zamorak in the [[Deep Wilderness Dungeon]] - {{Map|name=Wine of zamorak|mapID=26|3018,10353|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*[[Nature rune]]s by the [[Demonic Ruins]] in the [[Wilderness]] - {{Map|name=Nature rune|3311,3853,qty:3|3307,3859,qty:4|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*Nature rune north of [[Rellekka]] - {{Map|name=Nature rune|2671,3737,qty:2|2672,3738,qty:2|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}
*[[Teak plank]]s by the [[sawmill]] in [[Prifddinas]] - {{Map|name=Teak plank|2289,3357|mtype=pin|ptype=item|type=maplink}}

